rComments: Great profesor! Super passionate about what he teaches! Willing to really help you become better if you're willing to put in the effort!! Simple rule with him, work hard get good grades !

His class was a drawing class (not a surprise because he warns you about it day 1) & if you're not upto the task of truly learning something and gain actual architectural experience, then I suggest you drop out. Brian really helps form your ideas and brings out the best aspects of your project, & as long as you work hard, you get an amazing grade!
